==English==

===Etymology===
[[arm]] + [[wrestle]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[arm]]-[[wrestle]]}}

# A physical sport or game in which two contestants each rest an [[arm]] on a single surface by the [[elbow]] only and push on each other's locked [[hand]]s, until the loser is unable to keep his arm up anywhere in the air as the winner forces it down on the surface.

===Verb===
{{en-verb|arm-wrestl|es}}

# to compete in an arm-wrestle.

